Node "unknown1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Howdy, pardner. Got a few extra caps to spare for a friend that fell hard on ‘is luck?"
 NPCFemaleText "Howdy, ma’am. Got a few extra caps to spare for a friend that fell hard on ‘is luck?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, I’ve got exactly the amount I need. Sorry. " linkto "nocash1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I can help you. Care to share your story? " linkto "nomemo1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell you what, buddy. Take these 100 caps, go home and get your life straight. " linkto "caps100" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 100 link_next  } notes "PC must lose 20 caps and gain 5 Karma (or whatever)"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure, here’s 20 caps. " linkto "capslil" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 20 link_next  } notes "PC must lose 20 caps"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure, here’s 5 caps. " linkto "capslil" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 5 link_next  } notes "PC must lose 5 caps"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I’m not your friend, you stinking bag of Brahmin shit. Really, could your drunken ass be any more pathetic? " linkto "rude1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "nocash1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*sigh* Fair enough I guess. Sorry to bother you then. . [He turns to leave.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hey, I need you to answer some questions for me- [Grab his shoulder.]" linkto "done"  notes "This ends dialogue and Moses delivers unarmed critical hit to PC. After this node \"surprise1\" is auto-initiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure, “pardner”. Don’t let me stop you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
