Node "caps100"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[Stares at you unbelievingly.] Huh? You for real, pardner? Haven’t seen that amount o’ caps since my younger days… An’ now I know better than  to take’em. Here, take back this – [hands you 80 caps] – I’ll be just fine with the rest for a day or two. An’ I’ll drop a kind word for you here an’ there – that counts a lot when you’re new to a place. Now, if you’ll excuse me, gotta go an’ take my med’cine. [He turns to leave.]"
 NPCFemaleText "[Stares at you unbelievingly.] Huh? You for real, ma’am? Haven’t seen that amount o’ caps since my younger days… An’ now I know better than  to take’em. Here, take back this – [hands you 80 caps] – I’ll be just fine with the rest for a day or two. An’ I’ll drop a kind word for you here an’ there – that counts a lot when you’re new to a place. Now, if you’ll excuse me, gotta go an’ take my med’cine. [He turns to leave.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hey, I need you to answer some questions for me- [Grab his shoulder.]" linkto "done"  notes "This ends dialogue and Moses delivers unarmed critical hit to PC. After this node \"surprise1\" is auto-initiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure, “pardner”. Don’t spend it all in one place. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
