Node "rude1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, I guess I deserved that – what with me staring down the barrels of empty bottles insteada doing the job properly with a gun… Thanks for your honesty anyways. I won’t crowd your space any longer.  [He turns to leave.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hey, I’m not done with you yet, scum! [Grab his shoulder.]" linkto "done"  notes "This ends dialogue and Moses delivers unarmed critical hit to PC. After this node \"surprise1\" is auto-initiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah, take a hike! And next time you decide to drown in booze why not try the ocean for a change." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
